    <h1 style="padding: 10px; font-size: 75px; color: black; border: solid; border-color: black; background-color: lightblue;">5 star Weapons</h1>
    <div class="left"><div class="item1">
   This is the wolf's grave stone. It is a claymore and its good because it gives the character equipping the weapon lots of atk%. The base atk of the weapon is high and has atk% as the secondary stat. The passive gives you and your party even more attack so its just a good weapon for your active character and your team. This weapon also works on any claymore character so you can put it on anyone. 
    <p></p>
  </div></div>
  
  <div class="left2"><div class="item1">
    Wolf's Gravestone <p></p>
  <p></p>
  <div class="gallery">
    <img src="image/wolfs gravestone.jpg">
    <p></p>
    Base stats<p></p>
   Base atk: (lvl 1-90) 46-608<p></p>
   2nd stat: atk% (lvl 1-90) 10.8%-49.6%<p></p>
   Passive: <b>Wolfish Tracker:</b> Increases ATK by <b>20%.</b> On hit, attacks against opponents with less than 30% HP increase all party members' ATK by <b>40%</b> for 12s. Can only occur once every 30s.<p></p> The stats go up every refinement(everytime u get a duplicate of the weapon the stats go up if you fuse the weapon together)
  </div></div></div>
  <div class="left"><div class="item2"></div>
    This is the unforged. The unforged is really good under 1 condition, having a sheild. If you have a sheild on the character using this weapon will have a really big attack boost. But if you dont have a sheild the weapon can still be good but its not as great when u have a sheild. This is also a claymore weapon so any character that uses claymore's can use this weapon and be good if sheilded.
  </div></div>

  <div class="left2"><div class="item2">
    The Unforged
    <p></p>
    <div class="gallery">
      <img src="image/unforged.jpg">
      <p></p>
      Base Stats<p></p>
      Base atk: (lvl 1-90) 46-608<p></p>
      2nd stat: atk% (lvl 1-90) 10.8%-49.6%<p></p>
      Passive: <b>Golden Majesty:</b> Increases Shield Strength by <b>20%.</b> Scoring hits on opponents increases ATK by <b>4%</b> for 8s. Max 5 stacks. Can only occur once every 0.3s. While protected by a shield, this ATK increase effect is increased by 100%.<p></p> The stats go up every refinement(everytime u get a duplicate of the weapon the stats go up if you fuse the weapon together)
    </div></div></div>
